thread.title: Bucs Quarterback Jameis Winston Encourages Elementary School Girls to Be Silent, Polite, and Gentle
thread.title_full: Bucs Quarterback Jameis Winston Encourages Elementary School Girls to Be Silent, Polite, and Gentle

author: Dayna Evans
title: Bucs Quarterback Jameis Winston Encourages Elementary School Girls to Be Silent, Polite, and Gentle
text:
Jameis Winston, the 23-year-old quarterback for the Tampa Bay Buccaneers, spoke in front of a third-through-fifth-grade classroom in St. Petersburg, Florida, on Wednesday, and had some unfortunate suggestions for how boys and girls should act.

Video of the “motivational” speech was published on the Tampa Bay Times website.... More »
